就第一次在美国服务器下载挺快的，然后就非常慢。上传更不用说了，慢到无法使用。\r\n阿里网盘在国内上传下载非常快，但是国内上传，然后在美国服务器上下载就非常慢。", "content_rendered": "<p>试了 google drive ，从美国服务器上传文件也不快，下载倒是还行。\n不管是用 windows 客户端还是网页客户端上传都不快，几 G 内容要我等 2 个小时。\n在本机 mac （国内 ip ） 上上传速度可以接受，在美国服务器上下载速度也可以接受，无法接受的地方就是在美国服务器上上传，也不知道为什么那么慢。</p>\n<p>也用过阿里网盘，就第一次在美国服务器下载挺快的，然后就非常慢。上传更不用说了，慢到无法使用。\n阿里网盘在国内上传下载非常快，但是国内上传，然后在美国服务器上下载就非常慢。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1653779366, "replies": 33, "id": 855961}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_large.png?m=1644497171", "name": "fe", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_normal.png?m=1644497171", "title": "前端开发", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/fe", "topics": 2510, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Frontend", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_mini.png?m=1644497171", "stars": 1251, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 791, "parent_node_name": "programmer"}, "member": {"id": 555001, "username": "shanejix", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/shanejix", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/98fdfed56859f20a138c67aa5bf98ce4?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/98fdfed56859f20a138c67aa5bf98ce4?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/98fdfed56859f20a138c67aa5bf98ce4?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1630581243, "last_modified": 1630581243}, "last_reply_by": "creanme", "last_touched": 1653818242, "title": "前端如何尽可能多的减少 bug，大佬们讲讲你们的方法论呗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/855971", "created": 1653786627, "deleted": 0, "content": "bug 计入绩效，末尾淘汰\r\n\r\n一个 bug 搞得人整天都不好了\r\n\r\n😭", "content_rendered": "<p>bug 计入绩效，末尾淘汰</p>\n<p>一个 bug 搞得人整天都不好了</p>\n<p>😭</p>\n", "last_modified": 1653786627, "replies": 30, "id": 855971}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1650095309", "name": "create", "avatar_normal": "https://cd